    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "Kx7oUnHXo9KLoPGfZQzQAdSmF0bFpb2P6rCfl/WwfX0=",
    "originContent": "### How does this work?",
    "translatedContent": "### 这是如何工作的？"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
