  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "X8IWKier4ADSNKYaR4wIvF7eF9Goh+hNihFHNOSyohk=",
    "originContent": "When you send `s/i/n` in Discord, it modifies your most recent message using the [sed](https://www.gnu.org/software/sed/manual/sed.html) format. Specifically, it replaces the first occurrence of the second parameter (`i`) in the message with the third parameter (`n`).",
    "translatedContent": "当你在 Discord 中发送 `s/i/n` 时，它会使用 [sed](https://www.gnu.org/software/sed/manual/sed.html) 格式修改你最近的一条消息。具体来说，它会将消息中第二个参数（`i`）的第一个出现替换为第三个参数（`n`）。"
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
