  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "NgGnP7/9aj2Zth4yJPVTtbf7rPC/G1oC90TRoB/wjqk=",
    "originContent": "> If you run a Discord server, I highly recommend adding [FixTweetBot](https://github.com/Kyrela/FixTweetBot) to your server. It automatically modifies links to use embed fixers like fxTikTok, and is highly customizable.",
    "translatedContent": "> 如果你运营一个 Discord 服务器，我强烈建议将 [FixTweetBot](https://github.com/Kyrela/FixTweetBot) 添加到你的服务器。它会自动修改链接，使用类似 fxTikTok 的嵌入修复器，并且高度可定制。"
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "7xyvJ70ZQj3HeTT4AFPXHzvIB6lFTTvxV2WpJV5S7iA=",
    "originContent": "### Using Direct Embeds",
    "translatedContent": "### 使用直接嵌入"
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "gythoZgckoAeZVPYsbrRmYG+m6APQ9lVfFYvm2hMHBI=",
    "originContent": "Don't want all that statistic clutter on your embed and only want the video or image? Simply change your URL to `d.tnktok.com`",
    "translatedContent": "不想让嵌入中出现那些统计信息，只想要视频或图片？只需将你的 URL 改成 `d.tnktok.com`"
  },
  {
