  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "4YWD/+z2ihXFN7QZ5v3N83uOx2BdRzxVgeNn6TMT7Gs=",
    "originContent": "### \"I don't see the video's caption!\"",
    "translatedContent": "### “我看不到视频的标题！”"
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "BY2sPWie9p+fieQQdjeNg5L3gLSxRgItaB49HTh0P9U=",
    "originContent": "By default, we put the description into the `og:description` tag, but Discord removes that from the embed if there's a video inside the embed. We decided not to add it to the top like what [tfxktok.com](https://tfxktok.com) does to prevent the embed from getting too cluttered with hashtags.",
    "translatedContent": "默认情况下，我们将描述放入 `og:description` 标签，但如果嵌入中有视频，Discord 会移除该标签。我们决定不把它放在顶部，避免像 [tfxktok.com](https://tfxktok.com) 那样让嵌入被标签过多的标签堆满。"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "eRETuJNrN18+B3JcSnvcbZrxOuyQl3Mpxbh2AzcLriY=",
    "originContent": "However, we want to give users the option to add it in case it brings additional context to the video. You can change your URL to `a.tnktok.com` to add the description to the top.",
    "translatedContent": "不过，我们想给用户选项来添加它，以防它为视频带来额外的上下文。你可以将 URL 改成 `a.tnktok.com`，以在顶部添加描述。"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
