    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "Adjo3ImqJTP+nsuVw65mLQofZnXI0Z6xhCVdxkgMBUw=",
    "originContent": "### Changing to High Quality",
    "translatedContent": "### 切换到高质量"
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "esHRU1nxLqXFwwt6wxzXRHmjVFBj+PiqdsUF+FKUadE=",
    "originContent": "TikTok supports H.265/HEVC (High Efficiency Video Coding) which offers significantly better quality at the same file size compared to H.264, at the cost of compatibility. By default, we use H.264 quality since [many users report issues with embeds breaking with H.265](https://github.com/okdargy/fxTikTok/issues/14), but support enabling H.265.",
    "translatedContent": "TikTok 支持 H.265/HEVC（高效视频编码），在相同文件大小下提供显著更好的质量，但兼容性较差。默认情况下，我们使用 H.264 质量，因为[许多用户报告 H.265 嵌入出现问题](https://github.com/okdargy/fxTikTok/issues/14)，但支持启用 H.265。"
  },
  {
    "row": 73,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 74,
    "rowsha": "E1Rjqq6vwzFTPvTXsA975+5ZCGebbt6ayIPgPVQ4usc=",
    "originContent": "To enable high quality H.265 playback, add `?hq=true` or use `hq.tnktok.com`:",
    "translatedContent": "要启用高质量的 H.265 播放，请添加 `?hq=true` 或使用 `hq.tnktok.com`："
  },
  {
    "row": 75,
    "rowsha": "m4PpJSHh4b/8md8yPSfWMOmpBKEDfriCX4o9710jGk8=",
    "originContent": "| Before | After |",
